title: I am not able to join the Physics Wallah Yakeen batch due to some problems. Can I still be able to crack the NEET by self-studying and by seeing Physicswallah’s old recorded lectures? - Quora

response.answer_text: Yes you can in yakeen batch everything is same as youtube except no of questions practice tricks and test..else everything is same..just do onething that practice all pyq questions in atime limit and mug up ncert like hell😅though i am not eligible to advise you because i myself a neet aspirant..just gave my opinion…thankyou.best of luck
